# Copy to `.env.test` — NEVER commit this file. NEVER use production credentials.
#
# Staging project (recommended): create a dedicated Supabase project named e.g. "smart-garment-staging".
# Local Supabase: run `supabase start` then `supabase status` for URL + service_role key.

SUPABASE_TEST_URL=https://YOUR-PROJECT-REF.supabase.co
SUPABASE_TEST_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=your-staging-service-role-key-here

# Optional: reuse a fixed org for ephemeral integration tests (creates disposable data per run).
# The hand-crafted scenario seed uses fixed slugs money-staging-org-a / money-staging-org-b instead.
# SUPABASE_TEST_ORG_ID=
